date: Time of tweet

ğŸ§¹ Preprocessing
Dropped non-essential and null-heavy columns (user_location, user_description)
Cleaned text using:
Lowercasing
Removing URLs, punctuations, numbers
Stopword removal
Stemming (Snowball Stemmer)

